{"tid":1442634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日北角一行看似是另一場恐襲嘅導火線！實則危險萬分。","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:19:49.000Z","uid":167548,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4543a0b25b464ad614d8a5ac361ba84d33f01fce","tid":1442634,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:18:32.000Z","msg":"個班福建佬大多是內地落嚟，唔似新界鄉黑同黑警有咩群帶關係而<span style=\"color: red;\">有所顧忌</span> (有明顯證據葉虎參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 如果真是出左咩事到時嚟返個<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港黑警大陸公安合作</span>拉番晒班撚樣落嚟香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一個可能是一個重要萬分嘅劇本去反cap721政府嘅無為，<br />\n更重要是北角好多鋪頭都沒開, 入商鋪避都無得避<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時有咩事就真是<span style=\"color: red;\">橫死街頭</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港黑警大陸公安合作</span>捉返晒返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被spin去晒<span style=\"color: red;\">福建黑衣撕殺</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇本: <br />\n今次一定會有黑衣比人打比人斬, 全世界黑衣入北角增援！<br />\n一開始被斬黑衣是人是鬼無從稽考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n點樣阻止呢場必然之戰, 儘量黑衣減少前往北角<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n解法方法: <br />\n交比警方處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果繼續39分鐘唔到將會另一個核彈！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acc3eb9ed25afd56dcf30fc35f939c38f3cb872","tid":1442634,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi