s/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e9b130823a80fdc1d58d4040cdacc1594425630e","tid":1442634,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eedb77b6e1520f93d888e4e4ffca1fe8f947719","tid":1442634,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"政府一味拖，呢段時間示威者有咩要注意？他說：「政府知香港人怕暴力怕亂，又金魚記憶，齋拖已經成功一半㗎啦。只要打多幾次大交，大家就唔知道邊個啱邊個錯，最後示威者嘅支持就慢慢流失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442226/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442226/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bd307f8847c8f9450726217888eff3467bbd7cfb","tid":1442634,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:25:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ed6b0e9f9a6ce0029e23791f84baaaff236be78","tid":1442634,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"政府北角呢步棋 我地點行都反攻唔到<br />\n所以要好好防守 下一步將佢軍"}]}